  <brief_title>Effects of Metformin, Pegylated Interferon Alpha and Ribavirin for Chronic Hepatitis C With Insulin Resistance</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Metformin, Pegylated Interferon Alpha and Ribavirin for Chronic Hepatitis C With Insulin Resistance</official_title>
